Version 0.1.0
+ First release

Version 0.2.0
+ Fix the significant failure by replacing @ComponentScan to BeanDefinitionRegistryPostProcessor

Version 0.3.0
* Change group ID form com.github.wnameless to com.github.wnameless.spring
+ Fix the significant failure when port of any request is missing
+ Allow user to omit the very first character "/" in each bulk operation url

Version 0.4.0
+ Add @Bulkable annotation to provide better controls
+ Prevent user send bulk request which contains bulk API path
* Change project name from spring-batch-api to spring-bulk-api

Version 0.5.0
+ Add BulkApiService interface and the DefaultBulkApiService implementation
+ Add @AcceptBulk to provide more controls

Version 0.6.0
* Upgrade spring-routing-resolver to v0.4.0 (For @GetMapping, @PostMapping, @DeleteMapping, @PutMapping, @PatchMapping)
* Upgrade spring-boot-parent to v2.0.0

Version 0.6.1
* Fix @ReauestBody bug
- Remove overriding equals and hashCode in BulkApiException

Version 0.6.2
+ Support application context path
